---
const clientName = "Test Client";
const projectName = "Token Verification";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{clientName} - {projectName} Brief</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #0d0d12;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'Avenir Next', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .brief-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 800px;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .header {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }
    .client-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      background: rgba(255, 75, 43, 0.15);
      color: #FF4B2B;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    p.subtitle {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #aaa;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .content-section {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #FF4B2B;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #ddd;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .back-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 40px;
      color: #888;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .back-btn:hover {
      color: #fff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="brief-container">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="client-badge">{clientName}</span>
      <h1>{projectName}</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Confidential Project Brief</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Success!</h2>
      <p>The routing logic is working perfectly. You successfully navigated to this page by entering the correct token.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>How it works</h2>
      <p>This file is located at <code>src/pages/briefs/test-token.astro</code>. Because the filename is <strong>test-token</strong>, Astro automatically makes this page accessible at <code>/briefs/test-token</code>.</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/" class="back-btn">&larr; Back to Portfolio</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
